  <brief_title>Prevention of Mucositis in Patients With Head and Neck Cancer Treated With Radiotherapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prevention of Radiation-induced Mucositis in Patients With Head and Neck Cancer Treated With Radiotherapy : A Double-blind Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
