  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prevention of radiation-induced mucositis in patients with head and neck cancer treated with
      radiotherapy : A Double-blind Randomized Controlled Trial
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To compare the effect of each herb extracts in form of mouth wash to protect or delay the
      onset of the radiation-induced mucositis from the adverse effects of radiation therapy in
      patients with head and neck cancer.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
